 \"to\": 333}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 355}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 373, \"to\": 381}, {\"ngram\": \"Light\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Eurostar was notably dearer, as was myAirbnb, but when booking I had put it down to the time of year - not that a major sporting event was taking place in my chosen destination, at that exact same time.\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 397, \"end\": 405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.264955753241045e-13, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"myAirbnb\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 441}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 489}, {\"ngram\": \"year\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"a major sporting event\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 548}, {\"ngram\": \"my chosen destination\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 573}, {\"ngram\": \"that exact same time\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was only right before my departure, as I spotted the sea of Ireland flags at St Pancras, that I realised my error.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 664, \"end\": 671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9434935109988166, \"rank\": 0.059890702286535424, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my departure\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 638}, {\"ngram\": \"the sea\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 660}, {\"ngram\": \"St Pancras\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 691}, {\"ngram\": \"my error\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 717}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Ah well, it's too late now!'\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 749, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought, and took the plunge - after all, Paris is always a good idea, right?\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 794, \"end\": 799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.215493925728374e-39, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the plunge\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"a good idea\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, most people would have learnt from this mistake and checked to see if any big events were happening before making any future holiday plans.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most people\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 847}, {\"ngram\": \"this mistake\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"any big events\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"any future holiday plans\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, alas, I am not most people.\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1008, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most people\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get exclusive discounts withMetro Deals- save on getaways and spa days.\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1082, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"exclusive discounts\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"withMetro\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"getaways\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1067}, {\"ngram\": \"spa days\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Powered by Wowcher Bannatyne Spa: Spa day for two with treatments, lunch & prosecco - save up to 57% off.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1189, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wowcher Bannatyne Spa\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"treatments\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"lunch\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"prosecco\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 57%\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get deal now Mystery Escape: Hotel stay with return flights from as low as \\u00a392pp - save on worldwide holiday packages.\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"deal\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1199}, {\"ngram\": \"Hotel\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1225}, {\"ngram\": \"return flights\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1250}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00a392pp\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1271}, {\"ngram\": \"worldwide holiday packages\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get deal now Beach Retreat (Lanzarote): 4* Lanzarote beach holiday with flights - save up to 58%.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"deal\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1320}, {\"ngram\": \"Beach Retreat\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"(Lanzarote\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"4* Lanzarote beach holiday\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"flights\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 58%\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get deal now So again, in October last year, I decided to return to the city for a quick getaway.\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"deal\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"a quick getaway\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And again, I completely missed that theRugby World Cupwas taking place in Paris at that time.\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1585, \"end\": 1590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.215493925728374e-39, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1581}, {\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, I am not going to lie to you and tell you that in both instances I did not come across a single sports fan.\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1718, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both instances\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"a single sports fan\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1717}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But what I will tell you is this: there really were not as many as I had anticipated and I still very much got to enjoy the city despite all the chaos.\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1870, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"all the chaos\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And if reports from locals are anything to go by, the same can be said for Paris duringthe Olympics.\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1947, \"end\": 1952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.215493925728374e-39, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reports\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1886}, {\"ngram\": \"locals\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1898}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"duringthe Olympics\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Footage of Disneylandhas been circulating online, showing eerily empty rides and barely any tourists in the park, and restauranteurs in the city have complained that they are not getting the desired footfall they had hoped for from the Games.\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2216, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Footage\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1981}, {\"ngram\": \"Disneylandhas\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 1998}, {\"ngram\": \"eerily empty rides\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"barely any tourists\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2074}, {\"ngram\": \"the park\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2086}, {\"ngram\": \"restauranteurs\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2106}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2118}, {\"ngram\": \"the desired footfall\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2181}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A restaurant owner in the Latin Quarter told theBBCthat July had been 'catastrophic' for him and that it was one of the worst months he's encountered for 25 years.\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A restaurant owner\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2236}, {\"ngram\": \"the Latin Quarter\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"theBBCthat July\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"the worst months\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2350}, {\"ngram\": \"25 years\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2380}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hoteliers, meanwhile, grumbled that they 'did not gain anything from the Olympics', despite slashing their prices to entice tourists.\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hoteliers\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2392}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2446}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"their prices\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2496}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed, a friend of mine who resides in Paris confirmed that the 'market is way softer than predicted.'\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2558, \"end\": 2563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.215493925728374e-39, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a friend\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2534}, {\"ngram\": \"mine\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2542}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'market\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Several pals were unable to rent out their places and prices were well below expectations,' he explained to me.\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Several pals\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"their places\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2673}, {\"ngram\": \"prices\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2684}, {\"ngram\": \"expectations\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was announced years ago and suggested that everything would be booked up and extremely expensive, but it has not materialised.'\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2867, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Which all begs the question: is now the perfect time to visit Paris?\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2931, \"end\": 2936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.215493925728374e-39, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the question\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2896}, {\"ngram\": \"the perfect time\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 2921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are looking to go this week or you have already booked and have no interest in the Games, here are my top tips.\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 3057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no interest\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3021}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3034}, {\"ngram\": \"my top tips\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3056}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It goes without saying that a trip to Paris requires a pitstop in Montmartre, but it's especially worth the schlep up the hill during major sporting tournaments, as those crowds tend not to head that way.\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3097, \"end\": 3102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.215493925728374e-39, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3125, \"end\": 3135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montmartre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.325465265599933e-30, \"text\": \"Montmartre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montmartre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montmartre\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a trip\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3093}, {\"ngram\": \"a pitstop\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3121}, {\"ngram\": \"the schlep\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3173}, {\"ngram\": \"the hill\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3185}, {\"ngram\": \"major sporting tournaments\", \"from\": 3193, \"to\": 3219}, {\"ngram\": \"those crowds\", \"from\": 3224, \"to\": 3236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whilst there, duck intoLa Recyclerie- a cool little bar that was once a train station and is made from recycled materials - for a refreshing drink, and be sure to soak up the atmosphere and view from the Sacr\\u00e9-C\\u0153ur at sundown.\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3491, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Whilst there, duck intoLa Recyclerie- a cool little bar\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3320}, {\"ngram\": \"a train station\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3350}, {\"ngram\": \"recycled materials\", \"from\": 3368, \"to\": 3386}, {\"ngram\": \"a refreshing drink\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3411}, {\"ngram\": \"the atmosphere\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3450}, {\"ngram\": \"the Sacr\\u00e9-C\\u0153ur\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is advisable, however, that you avoid the Pigalle area near the Moulin Rouge, as this tends to get pretty packed with drunk tourists post-game.\", \"from\": 3493, \"to\": 3639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3560, \"end\": 3572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.767037137762903e-33, \"text\": \"Moulin Rouge\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moulin_Rouge\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Pigalle area\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3550}, {\"ngram\": \"drunk tourists\", \"from\": 3614, \"to\": 3628}, {\"ngram\": \"game\", \"from\": 3634, \"to\": 3638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Look, it ain't justEmily Cooperthat loves 5th and 6th arrondissement of Paris.\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3713, \"end\": 3718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.215493925728374e-39, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cooperthat\", \"from\": 3666, \"to\": 3676}, {\"ngram\": \"5th and 6th arrondissement\", \"from\": 3683, \"to\": 3709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In this neighbourhood, there is a wealth of culture to soak up - be it in the form of the Panth\\u00e9on or the famed Shakespeare and Company bookshop on the Left Bank.\", \"from\": 3721, \"to\": 3883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3811, \"end\": 3819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panth\\u00e9on\", \"score\": 0.9984280596889958, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Panth\\u00e9on\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panth\\u00e9on\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panth\\u00e9on\"}, {\"begin\": 3833, \"end\": 3844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Shakespeare\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.1041214468204374e-20, \"text\": \"Shakespeare\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Shakespeare\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Shakespeare\"}, {\"begin\": 3873, \"end\": 3882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rive_Gauche\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7661200977589348e-27, \"text\": \"Left Bank\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rive_Gauche\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rive_Gauche\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this neighbourhood\", \"from\": 3724, \"to\": 3742}, {\"ngram\": \"a wealth\", \"from\": 3753, \"to\": 3761}, {\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 3772}, {\"ngram\": \"the form\", \"from\": 3795, \"to\": 3803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And hey, if you really just want to be a basic (or ringarde) b***h - no judgement here, I promise - you can also go to the square where the Netflix hit was filmed, and see everything from Gabriel's restaurant to the boulangeriewhere Emily gets her morning pastries from, all ahead of season 4.\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 4178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4025, \"end\": 4032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.131054738314786e-16, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a basic (or ringarde) b***h - no judgement\", \"from\": 3924, \"to\": 3966}, {\"ngram\": \"the square\", \"from\": 4004, \"to\": 4014}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4057, \"to\": 4067}, {\"ngram\": \"Gabriel's restaurant\", \"from\": 4073, \"to\": 4093}, {\"ngram\": \"Emily\", \"from\": 4118, \"to\": 4123}, {\"ngram\": \"her morning pastries\", \"from\": 4129, \"to\": 4149}, {\"ngram\": \"season\", \"from\": 4169, \"to\": 4175}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Located in the 4th arrondissement, Le Marais is one of the chicest, prettiest neighbourhoods in the whole of Paris.\", \"from\": 4180, \"to\": 4295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4215, \"end\": 4224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Marais\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Le Marais\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Marais\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Marais\"}, {\"begin\": 4289, \"end\": 4294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.215493925728374e-39, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 4th arrondissement\", \"from\": 4191, \"to\": 4213}, {\"ngram\": \"the chicest, prettiest neighbourhoods\", \"from\": 4235, \"to\": 4272}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole\", \"from\": 4276, \"to\": 4285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to lots of cool coffee shops and eateries, the streets are full of independent boutiques and craft stores - a guaranteed Olympics-free zone.\", \"from\": 4297, \"to\": 4449, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 4300, \"to\": 4308}, {\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 4312, \"to\": 4316}, {\"ngram\": \"cool coffee shops\", \"from\": 4320, \"to\": 4337}, {\"ngram\": \"eateries\", \"from\": 4342, \"to\": 4350}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 4352, \"to\": 4363}, {\"ngram\": \"independent boutiques\", \"from\": 4376, \"to\": 4397}, {\"ngram\": \"craft stores\", \"from\": 4402, \"to\": 4414}, {\"ngram\": \"a guaranteed Olympics-free zone\", \"from\": 4417, \"to\": 4448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are few better things in life than buttery, flaky pastry.\", \"from\": 4451, \"to\": 4514, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"few better things\", \"from\": 4461, \"to\": 4478}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 4482, \"to\": 4486}, {\"ngram\": \"flaky pastry\", \"from\": 4501, \"to\": 4513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And luckily Paris is full of boulangeries and patisseries that serve just that.\", \"from\": 4515, \"to\": 4594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4527, \"end\": 4532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.215493925728374e-39, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"boulangeries\", \"from\": 4544, \"to\": 4556}, {\"ngram\": \"patisseries\", \"from\": 4561, \"to\": 4572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of my favourite places to hit up in the city includeBo&Mie,Stohrer,Ladur\\u00e9eandLe Pain Retrouv\\u00e9.\", \"from\": 4596, \"to\": 4695, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my favourite places\", \"from\": 4604, \"to\": 4623}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 4637, \"to\": 4645}, {\"ngram\": \"Stohrer\", \"from\": 4660, \"to\": 4667}, {\"ngram\": \"Ladur\\u00e9eandLe Pain Retrouv\\u00e9\", \"from\": 4668, \"to\": 4694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or, if I am feeling super fancy,Le Comptoir at the Ritz Paris.\", \"from\": 4696, \"to\": 4758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4752, \"end\": 4757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.215493925728374e-39, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In around 30 minutes, visitors can get from Paris to Versailles-Chantiers station - for a reasonable \\u20ac7.\", \"from\": 4760, \"to\": 4864, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4804, \"end\": 4809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.215493925728374e-39, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4813, \"end\": 4841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versailles-Chantiers_station\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Versailles-Chantiers station\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versailles-Chantiers_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versailles-Chantiers_station\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"around 30 minutes\", \"from\": 4763, \"to\": 4780}, {\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 4782, \"to\": 4790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simply hop on the RER C train (or the yellow line) and you will be transported to the grand suburb that was once home to kings Louis XIV and XVI.\", \"from\": 4866, \"to\": 5011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4993, \"end\": 5002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_XIV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.784635323889977e-16, \"text\": \"Louis XIV\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_XIV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_XIV\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the RER C train\", \"from\": 4880, \"to\": 4895}, {\"ngram\": \"the yellow line\", \"from\": 4900, \"to\": 4915}, {\"ngram\": \"the grand suburb\", \"from\": 4948, \"to\": 4964}, {\"ngram\": \"kings\", \"from\": 4987, \"to\": 4992}, {\"ngram\": \"XVI\", \"from\": 5007, \"to\": 5010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, you will likely have to book your tour of the palace in advance, as it gets pretty chocker on the day.\", \"from\": 5013, \"to\": 5120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your tour\", \"from\": 5047, \"to\": 5056}, {\"ngram\": \"the palace\", \"from\": 5060, \"to\": 5070}, {\"ngram\": \"advance\", \"from\": 5074, \"to\": 5081}, {\"ngram\": \"pretty chocker\", \"from\": 5094, \"to\": 5108}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 5112, \"to\": 5119}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But once you have your tickets sorted, you will be able to wander around the ridiculously ornate building and its manicured gardens for the day.\", \"from\": 5121, \"to\": 5265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your tickets\", \"from\": 5139, \"to\": 5151}, {\"ngram\": \"the ridicul